  "notebookEntry": {
    "content": "<h2>Rychlost</h2><p><strong>Rychlost</strong> vyjadřuje, jakou dráhu urazí těleso za jednotku času.</p><div style=\"text-align:center;margin:1.5rem auto;max-width:520px;\"><svg viewBox='0 0 420 130' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' style='width:100%;font-family:sans-serif'>\n  <text x='210' y='20' text-anchor='middle' font-weight='bold' fill='#1e40af' font-size='14'>Trojúhelník veličin</text>\n  <polygon points='210,30 130,110 290,110' fill='#eff6ff' stroke='#3b82f6' stroke-width='2'/>\n  <line x1='130' y1='77' x2='290' y2='77' stroke='#3b82f6' stroke-width='1.5'/>\n  <text x='210' y='68' text-anchor='middle' fill='#1e40af' font-size='22' font-weight='bold'>s</text>\n  <text x='175' y='100' text-anchor='middle' fill='#1e40af' font-size='22' font-weight='bold'>v</text>\n  <text x='240' y='100' text-anchor='middle' fill='#6b7280' font-size='18'>×</text>\n  <text x='252' y='100' text-anchor='middle' fill='#1e40af' font-size='22' font-weight='bold'>t</text>\n  <text x='360' y='55' fill='#374151' font-size='12'>v = s / t</text>\n  <text x='360' y='75' fill='#374151' font-size='12'>s = v · t</text>\n  <text x='360' y='95' fill='#374151' font-size='12'>t = s / v</text>\n</svg></div><h3>Vzorec</h3><div class='formula'>$$v = \\frac{s}{t}$$</div><table><thead><tr><th>Veličina</th><th>Symbol</th><th>Jednotka</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>rychlost</td><td>v</td><td>m/s</td></tr><tr><td>dráha</td><td>s</td><td>m</td></tr><tr><td>čas</td><td>t</td><td>s</td></tr></tbody></table><h3>Odvozené vzorce</h3><div class='formula'>$$s = v \\cdot t$$</div><div class='formula'>$$t = \\frac{s}{v}$$</div><h3>Převod jednotek</h3><div class='formula'>$$1 \\, \\text{m/s} = 3{,}6 \\, \\text{km/h}$$</div><div class='formula'>$$1 \\, \\text{km/h} = \\frac{1}{3{,}6} \\, \\text{m/s} \\approx 0{,}28 \\, \\text{m/s}$$</div><h3>Příklad</h3><p>Cyklista ujel 900 m za 3 minuty. Jakou měl průměrnou rychlost?</p><p><strong>Řešení:</strong></p><div class='formula'>$$t = 3 \\, \\text{min} = 180 \\, \\text{s}$$</div><div class='formula'>$$v = \\frac{s}{t} = \\frac{900}{180} = 5 \\, \\text{m/s} = 18 \\, \\text{km/h}$$</div>"
  }
}
